outputs.output_descr: Improved capacities of the third sector in the Transnistrian region of Moldova and increased citizen action as a result of CBMs implementation

project_descr: Address the needs of most vulnerable communities, with a specific focus on Transnistrian region of Moldova, by increasing their access to basic social and economic services, as well as to objective and diversified sources of information.
project_title: Support to Civil Society in Transnistria
